Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:12.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H94&\an8\3c&HFF00FF&}字幕由ACG12小站，_沉默似金制作，仅供学习交流使用，不得用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就这么喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是暗黑骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗啊 恶德之王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,召唤恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,死了回到斯卡尔赫大人的怀抱里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,被抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩毛毛虫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我说佐迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想从赛琳矿山出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经快四了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是毛毛虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再确认一下优先顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要我们五个人活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是救出蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然我会尽力而为 不过不可以乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿讨厌蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被蓝德说平胸 梦儿很受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就算让他别说了 蓝德也不听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要让梦儿喜欢上这种人 太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果梦儿 在这种地方孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会很不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想到蓝德现在 会是什么样就...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果因为这点小事就死了 他早就死了很多回了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 蓝德在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}外斯外斯外斯外斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没空这么干了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那种状况下一个人爬上来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是这样 那是非常了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,至少生命力极其顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他的韧性使我们不具备的资质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要活下去啊 蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧蓝德 蓝德去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,平胸...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}平胸平胸平胸平胸平胸平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,早知道就该摸一把平胸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,排气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要突然叫人名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我吓得都快死了白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,马利克·艾姆·帕尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是梦儿最后一支箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家往这边 梦儿也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能跑吗 蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在跟谁说话呢垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,马利克·艾姆·帕尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼眶有点湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上到处都很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我们活着重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不...不对 我才不想你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到不用再看到你们的脸了 我胸口就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口就怎么了 疼得快裂开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不...不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,胸...胸口就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,胸...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就叫 叫个几百回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,平胸平胸平胸平胸.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴好好呆着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说你不想治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不...不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 好像没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会欧鲁达那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要放松的话 等回到欧鲁达那再放松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德说「你是队长」 我思考着他这句话的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在我心里 说到队长的话就算马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要变得像马纳多那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这种心情 确实也是有一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多说过 谁都有擅长和不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多不擅长什么 我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有许多不擅长的事和不足的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴们会帮我弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这样就算维持了队伍的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我说一点都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,自己有没有尽到队长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 队伍能顺畅运转 是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我和蓝德也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗的时候能配合好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时用不了魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最多只能勉强用一次治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,需要找地方冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太懂魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不过席赫露看起来也快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小心不要刺激到小地精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,马利克·艾姆·帕尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead Spot受伤越多就越强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还...还要变强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该...该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能逃得掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一条路 肯定逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人 最起码要留下一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在思考之前 身体就动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 听不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别死啊 笨蛋哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下让我不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是魔鬼吗 混蛋蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然顽强的你这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我肯定不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,记得来驱散我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话应该能再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,直到死都要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好像停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,动得很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别去想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,天国...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛 给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead Spot呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫好烫好烫...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是赏金30金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等哈尔希洛醒了 大家再一起商量怎么分 蓝德说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他说因为哈尔希洛是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去接哈尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个接啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟Date Spet倒在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Date... Dead Spot？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,正好我的剑断了 这个挺趁手的就拿过来用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这个趁手...莫古索真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 啊 没有啦 这样直接用当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想送去锻冶店里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看来赏金的用途已经定好一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等完成了 要起个可爱的名字才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,菜刀一号之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可...可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 我帮你修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,身体熟悉的些微重量与感触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议地让人心情平静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,突然让我有了实感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了我听说了 小哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,居然干掉了Deat Spot 真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有掉小嫉妒 才没这回事呢尼日利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,莲司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莲司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多死后的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 莲司不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没能接受马纳多死了的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 谢谢你莲司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 今天我们请客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我有事想问马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你当队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会有时候觉得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛觉得难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是长高了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的自己和今天的自己是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的自己又会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每一天都活在当下 去见明天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来的 马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个世界生活的越久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就有一份记忆离得越来越远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说是我们原本所在的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从别的什么地方来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有个空洞 似乎忘记了什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我很不安 很焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从前是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,脚下踏着的石阶 吸入的空气味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我感觉自己现在确实就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:23:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也有不想忘记的事 也有不能忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:24.96,TitoloEP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&H14101A&\bord1.8\an7\blur5\3c&HE9EDEE&\fs70\pos(295.61,128.534)}明天见--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:24.96,TitoloEP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&H14101A&\an3\fs33\bord3.0\blur6\3c&HEEEBE9&\3a&H87&\pos(1224.904,561.667)}灰与幻想的\N格林姆加尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:35.72,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ふざけ合って笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:40.14,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}傷ついて泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:46.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}同じ時を生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:52.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}そんな一瞬が 日常が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:57.47,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大事な思い出へと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:07.08,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}変わりいく夜明けは奇跡になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:18.12,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}いつか見てた 空に映した
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:27.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕の影に 未来の風が吹く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:35.90,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明日またね 会えてよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:44.91,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}遠く遠く 歩いてきた道は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:51.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}また新しい世界ヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:11.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}出会い別れ超えてきたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:20.48,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}一つ一つ重ねてきた日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:26.57,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}もう失くさない記憶へ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:55.97,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}地平線に今を描いて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:04.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}次の朝が明日を連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:13.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}いつか先へもっと先へと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:22.37,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕のままで未来へ進んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:31.60,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明日またね会えて良かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:40.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}遠く遠く歩いてきた道は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:46.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}また新しい世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:35.72,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}时常互相开玩笑而忍俊不禁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:40.14,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}有时又因伤痛而暗自落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:46.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们彼此都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:52.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这样一个小小的瞬间 一份简单的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:57.47,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也能成为我们重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:07.08,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}看啊 逐渐浮现于天边的朝霞 宛若奇迹 照耀大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:18.12,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们曾经见到 那映照于天空之上的宛若奇迹 照耀大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:27.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们的背影 被从未来而至的清风吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:35.90,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明天见哦 能与大家相遇真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:44.91,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}回首而望 走过的路 何其漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:51.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也不忘记 再次向着新世界 迈出坚定的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:11.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}越过了时聚时别的时光 我们定将共同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:20.48,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}面对着重复着的每日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:26.57,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我再也不会 任其淡忘于记忆之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:55.97,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}绘出地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:04.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}下一道曙光 代表着的正是明天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:13.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}向着曾经期许的前方 为了更近一步而继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:22.37,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}就这样 向着未来前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:31.60,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明天见哦 能与大家相遇真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:40.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}回首而望 走过的路 何其漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:46.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也不忘记 再次向着新世界 迈出坚定的步伐
